{"tid":1771693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[奶共迪士尼]點解仲咁多人去睇Frozen？","createTime":"2019-12-06T04:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T04:15:02.000Z","uid":219969,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7eb2ecf65ce684fc97d3a12b3ec458eb7ff2701d","tid":1771693,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:58:40.000Z","msg":"迪士尼有幾奶共唔洗我多講<br />\n除咗撐共劉亦菲單嘢<br />\n之前迪士尼CEO仲話<strong>不會就香港示威事件發聲，因可能會損害迪士尼的利益。</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2480772/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2480772%2F&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScIRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=0f64b800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2480772/</a><br />\n<br />\n好啦咁當我以為大家會齊齊罷睇啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你打開個ig個撚個都走去睇Frozen</span></span><br />\n啲平時有去遊行嘅friend都話  <br />\n呢套戲真係好鍾意呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇辦法唔去睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等咗續集好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哦原來罷睇CCTVB就可以<br />\n奶共迪士尼就唔得<br />\n係咪因為CCTVB冇咁吸引<br />\n迪士尼好好睇就即刻個個忍唔住仆過去睇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌哂你哋老母呀！</span><br />\n咩叫骨氣呀？咩叫原則呀？<br />\n就係無論幾鍾意都唔要俾一分一毫呢間奶共迪士尼賺呀！<br />\n唔怪得之迪士尼CEO可以講埋啲咁嘅嘢唔驚激嬲香港人啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為佢知道一定大把人仆去迪士尼同睇佢啲戲呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我嚴正呼籲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔撚好再幫襯迪士尼</span></span><br />\n你嘅行為同幫襯撐警藍店冇分別<br />\n對你哋好失望，恥與為伍！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e772917fb408c6191beef70a66a09483c03e34a","tid":1771693,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8dd5c0170956f5599d3a4a0635d1b0c86654f504","tid":1771693,"uid":219969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:00:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">128  維園見！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sq0tVWk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSq0tVWk.jpg&h=1cdc8eb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbc5a815db7adb19f42b9a7605950270f832f107","tid":1771693,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:02:55.000Z","msg":"#BoycottMulan<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jb7sr3W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJb7sr3W.jpg&h=150d4eb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c12eb22602fcd44764c0c0b2c8f05d737356495","tid":1771693,"uid":245250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:19:00.000Z","msg":"12.8 維園見"},{"pid":"a1044d78f74f29c6432503fa7b27f0cf92f17e3e","tid":1771693,"uid":199590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:15:02.000Z","msg":"好睇就自然有人睇㗎啦，到時marvel出新戲咪又係一堆人衝去睇，你地咁鍾意反共，咪反飽佢囉，夠薑劇透埋添呀笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}